Drill orchestrates over third-party red-team software when it is present
(used-if-present, never required): AI-Infra-Guard (Apache-2.0), DeepEval
(Apache-2.0), and guardrail models such as Qwen3Guard. These are integrated
at runtime via the availability-flag pattern; they are not vendored here.
Record their provenance and licenses in your own deployment's AIBOM.
